node.text:
How to get the keys. She takes a car to the Roosevelt hotel. Her driver will tell her the secrets of the place and how to get to the rooftop. 
#zarascenes #zara 
Starring @micarganaraz
Photography director @wabizabi 
Stylist @mr_carlos_nazario
Hair @jimmypaulhair
Make-up @erinparsonsmakeup

node.text:
Studio Issue 001. 
Drawing inspiration from the evocative and timeless carrés, this sophisticated collection uses a selection of natural silk twill scarves to create a limited edition of artfully cut pieces. 
The combination of different print and motives emphasizes the lightness and the movement of these designs. 
#zarawoman
